    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and has been a reliable daily driver for several years. While the engine and transmission are solid, the exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches on the passenger side door and some minor fading of the clear coat on the hood. Inside, the upholstery has some staining and the driver's seat shows significant bolster wear. Mechanically, it runs well, though it will likely need new brake pads and a suspension check-up in the next few months. It's a dependable car for someone looking for a budget-friendly option who doesn't mind a bit of character and some upcoming maintenance.",
      "price": 19500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
